All INTERNAL requests for TOR data MUST, upon receipt, be directed to the Manager: Capability, Response and Operations, to determine if District, or Response and Operations, should reply. TOR data MUST NOT be EXTERNALLY released without the permission of the National Manager: Response and Operations.
QUERY: Incident Date >= 01/07/2016 + Incident Date <= 31/12/2016 + Status = Complete
